title: Mama Gogo
overview: Annie, a former singer from the '90s is passed down from her uncle an agogo bar called Papa Gogo. She decides to renovate it and starts hunting down her agogo boys. The bar eventually becomes well-known as Mama Gogo. However, a local mafia boss Chen and  Annie's frienemy, Tina who opens an agogo bar to compete with hers, always get in her way to success. Gather around and root for Annie! Let's see if the new mama can take control of the agogo kingdom.
